23
00:01:21,915 --> 00:01:23,625
Yes. And I picked this up

24
00:01:25,335 --> 00:01:26,753
on the way here.

25
00:01:27,545 --> 00:01:29,839
You said you use pencils at work,

26
00:01:29,923 --> 00:01:31,299
so I got this for you.

27
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:34,094
