28
00:01:47,690 --> 00:01:48,608
Thanks.

29
00:01:50,193 --> 00:01:51,444
I'll make good use of them.

30
00:01:52,237 --> 00:01:53,071
Okay.

31
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,865
