93
00:08:03,566 --> 00:08:07,904
We made a few house visits
and met his mom because of that.

94
00:08:08,613 --> 00:08:12,200
What other reason is there?
He just got lazy and didn't want to.

95
00:08:13,409 --> 00:08:17,163
In his case,
his mother is his only guardian,

96
00:08:17,246 --> 00:08:19,790
but she's too busy making a living.

97
00:08:19,874 --> 00:08:23,878
But that doesn't mean
we can just dwell on him for so long.

98
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:29,258
There was a claim
that he was harassed for a long time.

99
00:08:29,342 --> 00:08:31,010
That was from his mother, right?

100
00:08:32,345 --> 00:08:34,388
You probably already know this,

101
00:08:34,472 --> 00:08:37,058
but he's a Taekwondo blackbelt
and over 180cm.

102
00:08:37,141 --> 00:08:40,269
His past offenses are
for assault and extortion,

103
00:08:40,895 --> 00:08:42,480
so I don't really believe her.

104
00:08:53,324 --> 00:08:56,869
That was months ago and I already told
the detectives everything.

105
00:08:56,953 --> 00:08:58,204
Yes, I know.

106
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:03,209
But the minor who was driving at the time

107
00:09:04,335 --> 00:09:06,504
will be hospitalized for a long time.

108
00:09:07,505 --> 00:09:11,676
I'm sorry, but can I meet
the employee who was in charge then?

109
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:13,719
Jeez, I don't know.

110
00:09:13,803 --> 00:09:16,764
She was assigned
to another branch last month.

111
00:09:17,265 --> 00:09:22,687
Then can I get her contact information
or which branch she was assigned to?

112
00:09:23,896 --> 00:09:28,276
Working this job, I've seen lots of kids
turn themselves around and get better.

113
00:09:28,359 --> 00:09:30,778
But there are also
a lot of kids that don't.

114
00:09:39,537 --> 00:09:40,746
You asked for me, Judge Sim?

115
00:09:40,830 --> 00:09:44,542
Kwak Do-seok
won't be sentenced in this case.

116
00:09:44,625 --> 00:09:48,296
So please summon all the other children
to attend the next trial.

117
00:09:48,379 --> 00:09:49,505
And for that trial,

118
00:09:49,589 --> 00:09:52,383
have their guardians
and attorneys wait outside.

119
00:09:52,466 --> 00:09:53,801
Yes, ma'am.

120
00:09:53,884 --> 00:09:54,844
And…

121
00:09:55,511 --> 00:09:58,598
when you have time,
please check their social media

122
00:09:58,681 --> 00:10:00,641
to see if there's anything problematic.

123
00:10:01,142 --> 00:10:02,393
Yes, ma'am.

124
00:10:03,644 --> 00:10:05,187
SECOND CRIME, DESTRUCTION OF PROPERTY

125
00:10:13,195 --> 00:10:15,573
Why can't you take charge
of your fellow judge?

126
00:10:16,365 --> 00:10:20,661
Who's in charge of
the underage traffic accident case?

127
00:10:21,871 --> 00:10:22,747
It's me.

128
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:24,665
If he's not in charge,

129
00:10:24,749 --> 00:10:27,668
why is he going to the rental shop
and poking around there?

130
00:10:28,336 --> 00:10:30,046
The Civil Service Office is in chaos.

131
00:10:30,129 --> 00:10:32,465
The store called and threw a fit.

132
00:10:32,548 --> 00:10:35,801
That it happened months ago
and they suffered serious losses over it.

133
00:10:35,885 --> 00:10:38,220
