135
00:10:40,723 --> 00:10:42,850
Tell him to come to my office now.

136
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:45,311
I'll handle it myself…

137
00:10:49,023 --> 00:10:50,483
and warn him properly.

138
00:10:52,318 --> 00:10:55,446
Make sure you handle him right.

139
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:17,718
What were you thinking?

140
00:11:19,595 --> 00:11:23,474
I specifically told you to stop
and not to cross the line.

141
00:11:23,557 --> 00:11:24,642
Are you really

142
00:11:26,477 --> 00:11:28,020
going to end it like this?

143
00:11:28,771 --> 00:11:29,772
What?

144
00:11:29,855 --> 00:11:32,066
Mr. Seo told me everything.

145
00:11:33,693 --> 00:11:36,153
That Do-seok's mother filed a petition.

146
00:11:39,281 --> 00:11:40,533
And that she feels wronged.

147
00:11:41,033 --> 00:11:42,702
That's why I had to look into it.

148
00:11:42,785 --> 00:11:45,705
-This isn't your case!
-There was one more person.

149
00:11:51,585 --> 00:11:54,839
When Kwak Do-seok was there
to rent the car,

150
00:11:56,173 --> 00:11:57,800
he was with someone.

151
00:11:58,968 --> 00:12:00,136
Hey, wait.

152
00:12:03,305 --> 00:12:05,057
-Hye-jeong!
-Yes?

153
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:13,441
Hello, do you already have a booking?

154
00:12:14,191 --> 00:12:15,443
Well, no.

155
00:12:16,193 --> 00:12:17,069
Have a seat here.

156
00:12:17,737 --> 00:12:18,571
Okay.

157
00:12:19,739 --> 00:12:22,450
When the police were investigating,

158
00:12:22,533 --> 00:12:25,202
she was too flustered
that she forgot about the girl.

159
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:28,831
She went to the police later, but the case
was already sent to the prosecution.

160
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:33,919
It was from a distance,
so she wasn't sure.

161
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:39,967
But she thinks
it was one of the girls riding the car.

162
00:12:48,392 --> 00:12:51,061
She may be the key to this case.

163
00:12:51,145 --> 00:12:52,855
We need to look into it further.

164
00:12:55,900 --> 00:12:56,942
Judge Sim!

165
00:13:00,446 --> 00:13:02,907
I said Kwak Do-seok
wouldn't be prosecuted,

166
00:13:03,407 --> 00:13:07,203
not that I'd half-ass this case.

167
00:13:08,913 --> 00:13:11,123
His guardian filed a petition,

168
00:13:11,207 --> 00:13:13,334
and since I have knowledge of that,

169
00:13:13,417 --> 00:13:16,587
I need to find out
what exactly happened at the time

170
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,340
and who's accountable for what.

171
00:13:20,466 --> 00:13:22,384
Finding out the truth comes first.

172
00:13:23,302 --> 00:13:27,348
And following the proper procedures
is also a judge's duty.

173
00:13:28,349 --> 00:13:30,392
You don't have to
go poking around everywhere.

174
00:13:33,687 --> 00:13:35,397
I'm also doing my best

175
00:13:36,315 --> 00:13:37,650
as the judge in charge.

176
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:45,991
Okay, I understand.

177
00:13:52,373 --> 00:13:54,375
Hello, Judge Sim. This is Seo Beom.

178
00:13:54,458 --> 00:13:55,543
What is it?

179
00:13:55,626 --> 00:13:58,337
I checked their social media
as you requested.

180
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:00,214
Their attorney must have told them to.

181
00:14:00,297 --> 00:14:02,967
All their photos and videos
have been deleted.

182
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:05,177
Their accounts have been
completely deleted.

183
00:14:05,261 --> 00:14:07,805
Their public group account
has also been deleted.

184
00:14:08,889 --> 00:14:10,891
What should we do now?

185
00:14:14,186 --> 00:14:15,771
There was one more person.

186
00:14:15,855 --> 00:14:18,983
When Kwak Do-seok
was there to rent the car,

187
00:14:20,192 --> 00:14:21,861
he was with someone.

188
00:14:22,903 --> 00:14:25,364
She may be the key to this case.

189
00:14:25,447 --> 00:14:27,074
We need to look into it further.

190
00:14:36,292 --> 00:14:40,087
All of them had alibis
for when the car was rented.

191
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:42,965
Lee Nam-gyeong and Kang Tae-hun
were at an Internet cafe,

192
00:14:43,048 --> 00:14:46,468
and Kim I-seon and Baek Mi-ju
went home early to rest.

193
00:14:46,552 --> 00:14:48,220
Was anyone else with them at home?

194
00:14:48,304 --> 00:14:50,347
They both said they were home alone.

195
00:14:52,850 --> 00:14:55,269
ICU VISITING HOURS
YEONHWA HOSPITAL

196
00:14:56,770 --> 00:14:58,564
4:40 P.M.

197
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:18,918
Are you okay?

198
00:15:21,587 --> 00:15:22,671
You're…

199
00:15:24,715 --> 00:15:25,841
Wait.

200
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:20,312
YEONHWA DISTRICT COURT

201
00:16:22,856 --> 00:16:25,401
-Excuse me.
-Yes, Lieutenant?

202
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:28,237
Some girl left this.

203
00:16:29,655 --> 00:16:30,614
What is it?

204
00:16:30,698 --> 00:16:33,951
I don't know exactly,
but I think it's a USB stick.

205
00:16:34,034 --> 00:16:35,536
YEONHWA DISTRICT COURT
KWAK DO-SEOK CASE

206
00:16:35,619 --> 00:16:39,081
I'm supposed to discard it,
but I kept it just in case.

207
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:44,044
This was handed to you today?

208
00:16:44,128 --> 00:16:46,547
She came to the court
and gave it to the bailiff.

209
00:16:47,131 --> 00:16:50,217
I checked the security footage
and I couldn't see her face.

210
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:52,511
But she seemed about Kwak Do-seok's age.

211
00:16:53,303 --> 00:16:54,680
Her handwriting seems so too.

212
00:16:57,599 --> 00:16:58,684
For security reasons,

213
00:16:58,767 --> 00:17:02,855
I'm supposed to discard it immediately
instead of handing it to judges.

214
00:17:03,772 --> 00:17:07,276
But I saw it just in case,
and was shocked.

215
00:17:30,716 --> 00:17:32,051
