216
00:17:33,469 --> 00:17:35,137
-Is there no sound?
-No.

217
00:17:35,804 --> 00:17:38,015
It seems to have been recorded
on a cell phone,

218
00:17:38,098 --> 00:17:39,433
but there's no sound.

219
00:17:39,516 --> 00:17:41,143
If this actually happened,

220
00:17:43,062 --> 00:17:45,397
Kwak Do-seok's guardian's claims are true.

221
00:17:47,232 --> 00:17:49,985
But why isn't he fighting back?

222
00:17:50,069 --> 00:17:52,946
He used to be an athlete, didn't he?

223
00:17:59,536 --> 00:18:00,996
Judge Cha.

224
00:18:01,872 --> 00:18:02,748
Judge Cha.

225
00:18:03,665 --> 00:18:04,625
Judge Cha.

226
00:18:11,757 --> 00:18:15,135
Others may not know,
but I know how much Do-seok has changed.

227
00:18:17,346 --> 00:18:18,931
