228
00:18:19,890 --> 00:18:22,226
he was being helplessly beaten, but no.

229
00:18:23,477 --> 00:18:24,520
He held back.

230
00:18:25,771 --> 00:18:28,690
He knew that he'd stand trial again
if he fought back,

231
00:18:30,109 --> 00:18:31,568
so he just put up with it.

232
00:18:32,152 --> 00:18:34,905
He has no reason to forge an ID

233
00:18:34,988 --> 00:18:38,325
and illegally rent a car
to drive without a license.

234
00:18:38,408 --> 00:18:41,703
And the passengers
were those who beat him up.

235
00:18:41,787 --> 00:18:43,664
This doesn't make any sense.

236
00:18:45,791 --> 00:18:47,376
No, it doesn't.

237
00:18:48,127 --> 00:18:48,961
But…

238
00:18:50,462 --> 00:18:53,340
even if those kids assaulted him
or threatened him,

239
00:18:54,299 --> 00:18:55,717
it doesn't change the fact

240
00:18:56,593 --> 00:19:01,598
that a man is in critical condition
because of his driving

241
00:19:02,599 --> 00:19:07,104
and that he himself
rented the car illegally.

242
00:19:10,357 --> 00:19:12,901
We don't even know
where the video came from.

243
00:19:13,819 --> 00:19:15,195
We need to stay level-headed,

244
00:19:17,156 --> 00:19:19,032
especially at a time like this.

245
00:19:40,721 --> 00:19:41,805
This is Sim Eun-seok.

246
00:19:42,556 --> 00:19:44,725
Please take the original copy of the video

247
00:19:44,808 --> 00:19:47,227
and have it checked to see
if it's been fabricated.

248
00:19:47,311 --> 00:19:49,354
And please make a copy of it as well.

249
00:20:12,961 --> 00:20:14,630
What on earth are they saying?

250
00:20:21,511 --> 00:20:23,639
