What about the video of the assault?

252
00:20:26,308 --> 00:20:29,603
Yes, the video.
I got a response from the analyst.

253
00:20:29,686 --> 00:20:32,564
He said it wasn't edited or fabricated.

254
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:33,482
But…

