00:20:36,902 --> 00:20:38,570
-Good job.
-Sure.

257
00:20:38,654 --> 00:20:43,450
Huh? Gosh, you motherfucker.
Hey, you bastard. You son of bitch!

258
00:20:43,533 --> 00:20:46,161
Did you just dodge, you bastard? Did you?

259
